# Git commits — no Cursor co-author

When creating git commits in this repository:

- Do **not** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any other Cursor co-author trailer to commit messages.
- Commit messages should contain only the summary and body the user requested — no agent attribution lines.
